Rajasthan
Sep 21, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			A 16-year-old girl was allegedly kidnapped and gang-raped by three persons in Barmer district.

Based on the complaint of the father of the girl, police have arrested one of the accused.

According to the complaint, the girl was kidnapped in a SUV by the three youth yesterday when she was standing at a bus stand on her way to school, police said.

They took the girl to a deserted spot near Dudhiya-tala village and allegedly raped her, the police said.

The FIR was lodged at Chauhtan police station and police nabbed one accused, Sriram Bishnoi.

On her parents' complaint, police acted promptly and alerted nearby check posts. During the checking, Bishnoi was chased and arrested by police.

The other two accused are still at large.

